            <title>[HADOOP-11099] KMS return HTTP UNAUTHORIZED 401 on ACL failure</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HADOOP-11099</link>
                <project id="12310240" key="HADOOP">Hadoop Common</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The usual error, HTTP UNAUTHORIZED means is for authentication, not for authorization.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;KMS should return HTTP FORBIDDEN in case of ACL failure.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
